                <note rend="inline" type="source">861.77/1607c: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Consul at Harbin</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Jenkins</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1920-07-15T16:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 15, 1920—4 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>What is extent and influence of the authority exercised in Chinese Eastern
                    Railroad zone by Russian Consul over and above his functions as a Russian Consul
                    on Chinese territory and what are his official connections with the railroad?
                    What are his views as to (<hi rend="italic">a</hi>) Japanese (<hi rend="italic"
                        >b</hi>) Semenov (<hi rend="italic">c</hi>) control of the railroad?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Colby</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
